Status report of Yi Tong Tse on 2/8/99


The following items are completed in last week:

- The switcher task state machine: including the on channel and off channel
  processing, and the DTS locking of the two channels.

- Processing of splice command.

- Time base adjustment for the on and off channels so as to provide
  continuous time base in the spliced stream.

- Regeneration of missing PTS/DTS.

- Modified the parse routines to make them Endian independent.

